                                                <header class='clearfix'>
                                                <h1 class="title" id="page-title">#FreeExpressionIs </h1>
                                            </header>
                                                        <div class="block block-system block-main block-system-main odd block-without-title" id="block-system-main">
  <div class="block-inner clearfix">
                
    <div class="content clearfix base-wrap">
      <div class="view view-2014-splash view-id-2014_splash view-display-id-freeexpression_page view-dom-id-0b0070cab8f18c865047dabea96bc5fb">
        
  
  
      <div class="view-content">
      

<div id="free-expression-title-region">
<a href="https://www.pen.org"><img src="https://www.pen.org/freeexpressionimage/1.png"/></a>
</div>
<!-- <div id="free-expression-titlered-region">
<span style="font-weight:bold;">#FreeExpressionIs</span> a right every writer should enjoy.
</div> -->
<div id="free-expression-region">
<div style="color: #B83101;float: left;font-family: 'Sentinel A','Sentinel B';font-size: 30px;line-height: 25px;font-weight: bold;text-align: center;width: 100%;">
Can you describe what #FreeExpressionIs</br> in 100 characters?
</div>


<a href="http://ctt.ec/4Yi2A" target="_blank"><div style="padding-top:50px; margin-top:20px; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px; background: url('freeexpressionimage/2.png') no-repeat scroll 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);float: left;height: 272px;width: 283px;">
				<p style="color: #FFFFFF;font-family: 'Verlag A','Verlag B' !important;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;text-align: center;">
				In a tweet to</br>
				@PENAmerican,</br>
				finish the sentence</br>
				#FreeExpressionIs...</br>
				in 100 characters</br>
				or fewer.
				</p>
				<div style="float: left;padding: 25px 0 0 90px;width: 100%;">
				<p style="float: left;color: #FFFFFF;     font-family: 'Verlag A','Verlag B' !important;     font-size: 18px;">Tweet it!</p> 
				<ul style="padding: 0 0 0 5px;float: left;display: inline;list-style: none outside none;">
				<li style="float:left;"><img src="freeexpressionimage/8.png"></li>
				</ul>
				</div>
</div></a>


<div style="padding-top:50px; margin-top:20px; margin-right:20px; margin-bottom:20px; background: url('freeexpressionimage/3.png') no-repeat scroll 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);float: left;height: 272px;width: 283px;">

                 <p style="color: #FFFFFF;font-family: 'Verlag A','Verlag B' !important;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;text-align: center;">
				 Invite your friends!</br>
				<span style="color: #FFFF66;">Share your ideas</span></br>
